#Steps to setup serverside
# Babak Naderi (babak.naderi@tu-berlin.de)

1. Install MySQL, PHP, and a webserver (NGINX, or Apache)
2. Create corresponding users, and databases in the MySQL
3. Put the verificattion.php and admin.php in the corresponding folders with a proper access right (both will contain u/p for database) the verificattion.php should be reachable by all games.

4. edit both files to contain u/p of a correponding database account.

5. add the code from game.js to your JavaScript game:
 5.1.
 




